description:
Practical experience in Construction industry;
To plan, source and negotiate with new/existing supplier, in order to reduce the total cost of inventory;
Supply contract management and periodical review supplier performance;
Highly motivated and quality driven;
Higher Diploma in Logistic Management;
Less experience will be considered as Purchasing Clerk. 

We offer attractive remuneration package. Interested parties, please send full resume with present and expected salary to HR & Admin Dept.

